1
00:00:20,164 --> 00:00:22,024
(panting)

2
00:00:24,700 --> 00:00:25,800
D'oh!

3
00:00:26,081 --> 00:00:27,361
(tires screech)

4
00:00:27,407 --> 00:00:28,211
(grunts)

5
00:00:30,046 --> 00:00:31,646
(bull bellows)

6
00:00:35,156 --> 00:00:36,590
(all panting)

7
00:00:39,167 --> 00:00:40,024
(bellows)

8
00:00:40,050 --> 00:00:41,357
(snorts)

9
00:00:41,589 --> 00:00:44,989
<font color="#00FF00">♪ The Simpsons 25x16 ♪</font>
<font color="#00FFFF">You Don't Have to Live Like a Referee</font>
Original Air Date on

10
00:00:45,003 --> 00:00:48,303
